{"tid":1690804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反對打傷兇徒的人可唔可以入來解釋下","createTime":"2019-11-03T12:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T12:37:00.000Z","uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef593d2bbe71dbcadda215162b03df6c80348fc2","tid":1690804,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:22:34.000Z","msg":"今次係兇徒有呀媽生？驚打死人？定係「打返佢就變成同佢地一樣」呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n延伸討論<br />\n<br />\n1. 以兇徒嘅行為，他還應否繼續被看待成一個人？（從而用對人嘅大愛、處理方式？）<br />\n2. 斬人耳仔唔洗攞返佢命，咁洗唔洗攞返耳仔？<br />\n3. 打返兇徒就叫對方一樣？點解會將受襲者及其同伴同施襲者放喺同一標準？同埋點解係用行為而唔係動機去比較？即係南京大屠殺時殺返日本人=同日軍一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"fa5b9d9bdac6691fb9fbf1d09803adb37bc5fb67","tid":1690804,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:25:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4c90d17664c090f7f52c4ea0ff7e41bbac8a417","tid":1690804,"uid":275730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:26:46.000Z","msg":"簡單D, 如果你地覺得香港法制無辦法制裁兇徒 (i.e. POPO會放人), 咁你地覺得應該點做兇手先可以得到應有既懲罰?"},{"pid":"a58af3d2752c9859ae7783209b749b9bd5aadf55","tid":1690804,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:20.000Z","msg":"叫得出黑警還眼<br />\n又受唔住打鬥<br />\n受唔住就行開一邊 去遠啲冷靜下<br />\n阻頭阻勢 <br />\n係咪要下一個途人冇埋隻耳仔？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 受唔住 會轉頭走 順便睇下附近有冇狗<br />\n<br />\n下次會拉埋你地走<br />\n真係好撚煩"},{"pid":"e220ea36d623b0ac02c2f72062e150f699b51615","tid":1690804,"uid":14478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"Tolerate the intolerance <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf3b5838b9ecfad46ceb70ebd120f6b15855fdd9","tid":1690804,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4c90d17664c090f7f52c4ea0ff7e41bbac8a417","tid":1690804,"uid":275730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"rep